This product includes software derived from pyEzvizApi
(https://github.com/RenierM26/pyEzvizApi), Copyright the pyEzvizApi authors,
licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.

Specifically:

- The EZVIZ Image-Encryption video decryption in `scripts/ezviz_decrypt.py` and
  `custom_components/ezviz_stream/decrypt.py` is an independent implementation whose
  algorithm is derived from `pyezvizapi.stream.decrypt_hikvision_ps_video`.
- The cloud-replay wire protocol in `custom_components/ezviz_stream/cloud_replay.py`
  (frame framing, the open/heartbeat XML control messages, and the message reader) is
  ported from the cloud-replay functions in `pyezvizapi.stream` (e.g.
  `download_ezviz_cloud_replay`).

pyEzvizApi is used only as a development/test dependency (a protocol reference and
decryption oracle); it is NOT a runtime dependency.
